values:
So yeah, I live in this tiny two bedroom apartment, right?

Well, the people who live there is me, Jackalope, and Brain.

We've been splitting the bills and it's relatively peaceful here.

I don't know how, but my two sisters, Megan and Sammi, convinced us three guys that they could live with us.

Five people in a tiny two bedroom apartment.

Oh, the chaos that shall ensue.

<center>Hey everyone, this is my journal, and hey.

Do comment.
Do friend me.
Do read.
Thanks.</center>
